fields.name: Doctors Without Borders
fields.mission_statement: Provides emergency medical care to people affected by conflict, epidemics, disasters, or exclusion from healthcare.

fields.name: International Rescue Committee
fields.mission_statement: Responds to the world's worst humanitarian crises and helps people to survive, recover, and gain control of their future.

fields.name: Oxfam
fields.mission_statement: Works to end the injustice of poverty through development programs, public education, and emergency assistance.

fields.name: CARE International
fields.mission_statement: Fights global poverty and provides disaster relief with a focus on empowering women and girls.

fields.name: Mercy Corps
fields.mission_statement: Helps people in the world's toughest places survive the crises they confront and turn them into opportunities for progress.

fields.name: Save the Children
fields.mission_statement: Supports children in crisis with health care, education, and protection from harm.

fields.name: World Vision
fields.mission_statement: A Christian humanitarian organization dedicated to working with children, families, and communities to overcome poverty and injustice.

fields.name: Red Cross
fields.mission_statement: Provides emergency assistance, disaster relief, and education in communities around the world.

fields.name: Action Against Hunger
fields.mission_statement: Combats hunger and provides access to clean water, food, and healthcare for vulnerable communities worldwide.

fields.name: Relief International
fields.mission_statement: Partners with communities impacted by conflict, climate change, and disaster to deliver life-saving aid and build resilience.
